fr.univrouen.umlreverse.ui.component.common.relation

Interface IRelationGraphic

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISelectionableEntityGraphic
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AClassRelationGraphic, ARelationGraphic, NoteRelationGraphic, RelationGraphic, RelationGraphic

    public interface IRelationGraphic
extends ISelectionableEntityGraphic
    Graphic relation of uml diagram. It contains two ArrowHead, one ArrowBody, name and one controller.
